# Linear Tickets for lit-node-express

When creating or moving Linear issues related to this repository (lit-node-express), always assign them to the **CPL (Chipotle)** team.

- Use `team: "CPL"` or `team: "Chipotle"` when creating issues via the Linear MCP
- When moving existing issues to this repo's team, update them to the CPL team
